      • buildObjects

        public ComponentObject[] buildObjects(java.util.List<VectorObject> vecObjs,
                                      MaplyTileID tileID,
                                      MaplyBaseController controller)
        Description copied from interface: VectorStyle
        Construct objects related to this style based on the input data. This is where we build the visible objects for the data corresponding to our style.
        Parameters:
        vecObjs - The vector objects we'll build a visual representation for.
        tileID - The tile we're building, if this is used by a tile source. If not, this is null.
        controller - The MaplyBaseController to use when building the visual representation.
        Returns:
        The ComponentObjects created when building a visual representation.
